  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This project will determine the incidence of sexual dysfunction in patients with chronic&#xD;
      liver disease, through questionnaires. The questionnaires have been designed to assess&#xD;
      several facets of sexual health, e.g. libido, physical symptoms, depression, etc. 150&#xD;
      patients in our liver outpatient department, and 150 healthy volunteers will be asked to fill&#xD;
      in the questionnaire in paper form. The results of this project will be used to produce&#xD;
      patient resources, advice sheets and educational materials for patients with chronic liver&#xD;
      disease. There is also scope to consider possible interventions in the future to improve&#xD;
      sexual dysfunction in patients with chronic liver disease.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
